summary: An ordinance relating to and providing for the licensing and regulating of certain occupations, businesses, vocations, trades, callings, amusements, places of amusement, exhibitions, entertainments, animals, motor vehicles, boats, places and establishments, and amending Ordinance No. 48022 by adding thereto a new section to be known as Section 183 and 1/3 relating to the transfer of pawnbroker's licenses.
